CorrectionProposer - Class in spellChecker
The awt window showing the word to be correct and editable textfield to enter correction This is a frame and is set up in constructor, the window will close once the correction has been proposed.
CorrectionProposer(String) - Constructor for class spellChecker.CorrectionProposer
Constructor of the class, setting the display of components it takes a string for the wrong word display empty textfield for correction
